    "description": "KAZEKAO is a fast-paced, challenging 2D platformer that will put your precision and speed to the test. Step into the paws of the blue cat Kazekao on a mission to retrieve Grandma Miauko's lost cakes scattered across 8 uniquely designed levels. Each level demands quick reflexes and perfect timing as you dash, jump, and maneuver through obstacles and enemies.<br><br>The game combines tight controls with increasingly difficult levels, creating a satisfying experience for those who love a good test of skill. Can you find all the cakes and return them to Grandma Miauko before time runs out?<br>Prepare to dive into a world where every second counts, and every move matters.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202810/extras/4dcadf74c10dd6bad8f9dc718fddbbf3.poster.avif?t=1727120019\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202810/extras/4dcadf74c10dd6bad8f9dc718fddbbf3.webm?t=1727120019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202810/extras/4dcadf74c10dd6bad8f9dc718fddbbf3.mp4?t=1727120019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Precision Platforming</strong></h2>Navigate through tight spaces with smooth, responsive controls.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Speedrun</strong> </h2>Challenge yourself to beat your best times.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>8 Unique Levels</strong> </h2>Each level presents obstacles and challenges to master.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Charming Pixel Art</strong> </h2>Enjoy a retro-inspired game with charming pixel art graphics.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Achievements</strong> </h2>Challenge yourself by trying to unlock more than 20 achievements!",
